com.mixer.interactive.resources.control

Class InteractiveControl<T extends InteractiveResource<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mixer.interactive.resources.InteractiveResource<T>
      • com.mixer.interactive.resources.control.InteractiveControl<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IInteractiveCreatable, IInteractiveDeletable, IInteractiveUpdatable, Comparable<InteractiveControl>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ButtonControl, JoystickControl

    public abstract class InteractiveControl<T extends InteractiveResource<T>>
extends InteractiveResource<T>
implements IInteractiveCreatable, IInteractiveDeletable, Comparable<InteractiveControl>
    The abstract class InteractiveControl is the superclass for all controls on the Interactive service.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Microsoft Corporation
    See Also:
    ButtonControl, JoystickControl
